interpretation: The "file cabinet" card represents organization, order, and structure. It suggests the need to sort through and categorize aspects of your life, whether it be physical possessions or mental clutter. This card can also indicate a need to keep secrets or information confidential, as a file cabinet is a secure storage unit. It may also suggest the need to access past memories or information in order to move forward in a situation. The "file cabinet" card reminds you to take the time to organize and prioritize, as it can lead to greater efficiency and clarity.
